sub_title: Biology and Science Communication and Society MSc Student at Leiden University
summary: I am currently pursuing a master's degree in Biology at Leiden University with a specialization in science communication and society. Along with my studies, I am also gaining hands-on experience through an internship researching natural products and biosynthetic gene clusters. This experience has enabled me to enhance my understanding of the intricate mechanisms within the field of biology and develop a greater appreciation for the significance of communicating scientific ideas with clarity and precision.
